               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Gabra Manfas Qǝddus “Vita of Gabra Manfas Qǝddus” (fols.
                     1ra-106vb, 115ra-115vb, 114ra-114vb, 117ra-118ra), incomplete (incipit missing)
                     and fols. misplaced
 II) Taʾammǝra Gabra Manfas Qǝddus “Miracles of Gabra
                     Manfas Qǝddus”: 12 miracles (fols. 118rb-122vb, 116ra-116vb, 107ra-113vb,
                     123ra-137rb), fols. misplaced
 
 colophon.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>In Text II, miracles 3, 5, 9 and 12 are not numbered. The numeral for
                        miracle 11 is not readable.</note>
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1"> Colophon: <locus from="117vb" to="118ra">117vb-118ra</locus>. <locus target="#117vb">117vb</locus>: ተፈጸመ፡ በዝየ፡ ገድለ፡
                        አቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ መን[<locus target="#118ra">118ra</locus>]ፈስ[፡] ቅዱስ፡ … ለጸሐፊሃ፡ ኢያሱ።
                        ወለዘአጽሐፎ፡ ወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡  አሜን፨ The note mentions the scribe ʾIyasu and
                        the commissioner of the Ms. Walda Giyorgis. </colophon>
                  </msItem>
                  
               </msContents>
