                           <signatures> Decorated <note>- Decorated quire marks are written (in
                                 black) in the upper and lower left and/or right margins:
 ፭:
                                    <locus target="#33r">33r</locus>, 40v; ፮: <locus target="#47v">47v</locus>; ፯: <locus target="#49r">49r</locus>, 56v; ፰: fols
                                 48r, 65v; ፱: <locus target="#57v">57v</locus>, 66r; [፲]: <locus target="#74r">74r</locus>, 83v; ፲፩: <locus target="#84r">84r</locus>, 91v; ፲፪: <locus target="#92r">92r</locus>, 99v;
