                           </signatures>
The structure of quires cannot be established
                                 due to present condition of the Ms. The quire marks written and
                                 readable on some fols. incude the numbers from 5 to 15.
                        </collation>
                        <condition key="deficient">The original sewing is for the most part missing.
                           The Ms. has been resewn with recent threads.
 Many fols. are
                           misplaced, some are missing at the beginning (the incipit of Text I is
                           lost) and possibly somewhere else (e.g., between <locus from="40vb" to="41ra">40vb-41ra</locus>).
 Most of the fols. are affected by
                           humidity, some fols. (e.g., <locus target="#129r">129r</locus>) or
                           passages are unreadable.</condition>
