               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origPlace>
                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0216MGM">Mǝʾǝsar Gʷǝḥila Qǝddus Mikāʾel / MGM</placeName>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1700" notAfter="1800">18th cent. (?)</origDate>
                  </origin>
               <provenance>Walda Giyorgis is mentioned as the
                     commissioner of the Ms. on 118ra (in the
                     colophon of Text I), and in supplication formulas throughout the Ms. In the
                     supplication formula at the end of Text II, on 137rb, he is also mentioned together with his children ʾArqǝdewos
                     and ʾAmonyos (their names are also on 132ra).</provenance></history>
